<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(109, 123, 120); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240116/1705387015601012511.jpg" title="1705387015601012511.jpg" alt="1705387015601012511.jpg" width="600" height="353" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 353px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(109, 123, 120); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">亲爱的校友：</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(109, 123, 120); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">岁月如歌，韶光流转，传母校之恩，承校友之情!一生季念，一脉相延!蹉跎的岁月，不变的友谊!时光不老，我们不散!但学院老师一直在关注着你们，为你们的奋斗拼搏鼓励喝彩。为你们的奉献成功喜悦自豪，在此，我们勤向追梦在各条战线上的校友们致以诚挚的问候！</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240116/1705387054216012324.jpg" title="1705387054216012324.jpg" alt="1705387054216012324.jpg" width="600" height="338" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 338px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(109, 123, 120); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">学院发展包含广大校友的智慧和心血，浸润着每一位校友的爱和关心。任凭时光流逝，母校及老师、同窗都是校友心灵深处纯真而永恒的温馨记忆。为进一步凝聚校友力量、促进学院和校友间的联系，请各位校友扫描专用二维微码填写信息，并帮忙转发。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(109, 123, 120); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我们郑重承诺：校友信息将严格保密，仅用于加强学院和校友的沟通联络。感谢各位校友的支持！如有未尽事宜可拨打电话：曹老师13077923100，本次征集长期有效。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240116/1705387092370024723.jpg" title="1705387092370024723.jpg" alt="1705387092370024723.jpg" width="600" height="450" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 450px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(109, 123, 120); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">亲爱的校友，学院期待你们的加入。让我们一起聚沙成塔、集腋成裘，共同谱写一曲永恒的校友情！恭祝各位校友身体健康，事业顺利，阖家幸福！</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(109, 123, 120); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240116/1705387145617027895.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 169px;" title="1705387145617027895.jpg" width="300" height="169" border="0" vspace="0" alt="1705387145617027895.jpg"/><img src="/data/upload/img/20240116/1705387146342042764.jpg" title="1705387146342042764.jpg" width="300" height="163" border="0" vspace="0" alt="1705387146342042764.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 163px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240116/1705387146344032973.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 169px;" title="1705387146344032973.jpg" width="300" height="169" border="0" vspace="0" alt="1705387146344032973.jpg"/><img src="/data/upload/img/20240116/1705387146387090200.jpg" title="1705387146387090200.jpg" width="300" height="168" border="0" vspace="0" alt="1705387146387090200.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 168px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(109, 123, 120); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">附件：</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: rgb(109, 123, 120); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240116/1705387287774038813.jpg" title="1705387287774038813.jpg" alt="1705387287774038813.jpg" width="600" height="600" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 600px;"/></span><br/></p>